OL,3,CLib Dems lose majority control of Hull
OL,4,Cas Reform wins 10 seats
OL,6,FThe Liberal Democrats have lost
OL,7,Foverall control of Hull City council,
OL,8,Fbut remain the largest party despite
OL,9,Fpressure from Reform UK.
OL,11,FMike Ross, Liberal Democrat Council
OL,12,FLeader of Hull City Council, described
OL,13,Fthe seats held by the party as a
OL,14,F"tremendous testament" to the work the
OL,15,Fparty does.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
