FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1778223659
OL,3,CLib Dems lose majority control of Hull
OL,4,Cas Reform wins 10 seats
OL,6,FHe said: "If you look at the political
OL,7,Fcontext of the country and in Hull,
OL,8,Fthe fact that we are winning seats
OL,9,Fstill here in Hull is a tremendous
OL,10,Ftestament to the work we do here and
OL,11,Fthe fact that people like what Liberal
OL,12,FDemocrats have to offer."
OL,14,FHowever, Richard Christopher Kelly,
OL,15,Ftold ITV Calendar that Mike Ross' days
OL,16,Fwere "numbered". He said: "Mike Ross
OL,17,Fdays are numbered, yeah pack your
OL,18,Fsuitcase empty your little desk, mate
OL,19,Fyou're gone."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
