CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1778223659
OL,3,CLib Dems lose majority control of Hull
OL,4,Cas Reform wins 10 seats
OL,6,FMr Kelly, who is the Chair for Reform
OL,7,FUK Hull Party described the reform
OL,8,Fparties success as "viral".
OL,10,FKarl Turner, Independent MP for Hull
OL,11,FEast, described the national picture
OL,12,Fas "a terrible night for labour".
OL,14,FThe backbench MP was suspended from
OL,15,Fthe Labour party in March. He said:
OL,16,F"It's not surprising, we expected it
OL,17,Fbe a bad night and these are the times
OL,18,Fwhere the electorate kick the
OL,19,Fgovernment - but it is worse than we
OL,20,Fexpected.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
