OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1778223659
OL,3,CLib Dems lose majority control of Hull
OL,4,Cas Reform wins 10 seats
OL,6,F"I think people expected change and we
OL,7,Fare not changing things fast enough
OL,8,Ffor them".
OL,10,FOne unnamed Lib Dem councillor who
OL,11,Flost his seat to Reform, explained to
OL,12,Fme how he "saw it coming" and asked
OL,13,Fthe new member "to be kind to the
OL,14,Fpeople in (his former ward".
OL,16,FBut how connected are people with
OL,17,Flocal politics?
OL,26,@uD@POUvD@KpmvD@[O]
