OL,3,CLib Dems lose majority control of Hull
OL,4,Cas Reform wins 10 seats
OL,6,FOne surprise perhaps, David Prescott,
OL,7,FJohn Prescott's son didn't manage to
OL,8,Ftake his seat for the Greens in the
OL,9,FSutton Ward - this again went to
OL,10,FReform UK.
OL,12,FIt was quite impossible to guess what
OL,13,Fwould happen at the Guildhall.
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
